{"tid":1358725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周日上環衝突 警未有示警橋上向下開槍 14人受傷","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:17:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65d2ee145eee77306180324aa3e80d813db778da","tid":1358725,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/20791_240719b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F20791_240719b.jpg&h=6ee249d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周日反修例遊行後，大批示威者集結上環中聯辦附近，當晚警方多次施放催淚彈及發射橡膠子彈驅散。《now》新聞台記者拍到，有速龍小隊人員在中區警署外天橋上向下面的示威者開槍，事前未有示警。香港人權監察羅沃啟批評警方做法不能接受，認為警方當晚使用的暴力，相較於612金鐘衝突並無改善，亦不恰當。香港人權監察在7月21日晚上有派員留意有關情況，發現有很多警員身上沒有佩戴委任證或警員編號，重申應成立獨立調查委員會調查這些情況。<br />\n<br />\n記者向警方查詢，當晚施放多少枚催淚彈、發射多少橡膠子彈和布袋彈等，以及是否未有警示在橋上開槍，暫時未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/20791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F20791&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=3b00e9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/20791</a>"},{"pid":"301fc157651d31713d71f9b6337baa4c45fca85e","tid":1358725,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4fcbeb24d0315bf98a7d3e36ad1e4cbdcfda1c8","tid":1358725,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1SWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=c547e4c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"}]}